Interface AnnotationTypeDeclaration

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Declaration, InterfaceDeclaration, MemberDeclaration, TypeDeclaration
    Deprecated. 
    All components of this API have been superseded by the standardized annotation processing API. The replacement for the functionality of this interface is included in TypeElement.

public interface AnnotationTypeDeclaration
extends InterfaceDeclaration
